(63, 'Fadhlihi', 'Ramadhan', 'fadhli.harianjogja@gmail.com', '0895 3666 6373 9', 'Media Strategist', 'Harian Jogja', 'business', 'Hi Linknet Team,\r\n\r\nI’m Fadhli from Harian Jogja (Bisnis Indonesia Group). For 16 years, we’ve been a trusted communication consultant and multi-platform media leader in Yogyakarta.\r\n\r\nWith our deep local insights and credible ATL/BTL/TTL channels, we’d love to discuss a potential collaboration to boost Linknet’s brand awareness locally or nationwide.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to your response!\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\n\r\nFadhlihi Ramadhan\r\nMedia Strategist | +62 8953 6666 3739', '180.254.126.3', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '2026-03-10 08:28:49', '2026-03-10 08:28:49', '2026-03-10 08:28:49'),
